    "nb_messages": 0x19,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "*sniff* *sniff*<CR>Huh? Something smells delicious."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x1a0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hey, Ayesha. Perfect timing."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "I was just about to have lunch.<CR>Would you like to join me?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x194,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Well...I was planning on skipping lunch today."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Why? You won't have enough energy if you don't eat properly."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "No matter what you do, your body is an important asset."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x38,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Hehe, well, umm...I'm starting to deal with a little weight problem..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "You've gained weight?<CR>It doesn't seem like it..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x39,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "But like, I've gained a little weight in places you can't see..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x126,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "A little? I don't think a little is much of a problem."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Buuut, it still matters. I am a girl, after all."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x128,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "With a body like yours, I think it's weird to worry about your weight."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Hrgh... But still, it's better to be lighter..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "No! While you're traveling, it's very important to maintain your peak physical condition."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x78,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "I've never heard of someone being on a diet while they're traveling before!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "But, but, still...I can't gain any more weight..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x15e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, so it means that much to you?<CR>Girls are really confusing..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x15f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Hmm...but it really doesn't seem like you've gained any weight..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x160,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Actually, it looks like you've lost weight..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Huh...? Really...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Yup. Maybe you've gained more muscle since you started traveling?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "I-I wonder... But that still doesn't change the fact that I weigh more now..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "It's healthy, and that's all that matters. Now, make sure you eat your lunch."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "I'll share with you, so come here."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, it looks delicious.<CR>Well, if you insist!"
        }
    ]
}